35 or before January 1 of the year in which application for the exemption under this
36 paragraph is made is granted an exemption on that person's homestead from all Gordon
37 County school district ad valorem taxes for educational purposes in the amount of
38 $125,000.00 of the assessed value of that homestead. The value of that property in excess
39 of such exempted amount shall remain subject to taxation."
